{"tid":1151534,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[劇透][理性學術討論]Iron man係電影嘅實力有幾高","createTime":"2019-05-12T14:44:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T14:57:07.000Z","uid":105396,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"20310d46f99024f7b472cb5a7c7f2dc5d47fc234","tid":1151534,"uid":105396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T14:44:20.000Z","msg":"係avengers3入面iron man可一打到thanos流一滴血<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=osSJhXruEzU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DosSJhXruEzU&d=gf59OkzbMHBVvJ2bZZ4HaqjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=89dc7750\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=osSJhXruEzU</a><br />\n而thanos就只係徒手，就可以將vision頭上嘅mind stone格硬拎落來(vision個身係用同captain個盾一樣硬嘅金屬Vibranium造)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PDVvO1z5pnM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPDVvO1z5pnM&d=gf59OkzbMHBVvJ2bZZ4HaqjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=4bcfed15\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PDVvO1z5pnM</a><br />\n咁就已經代表thanos&gt;Vibranium<br />\n而iron man有能力打到thanos流血<br />\nthanos&gt;iron man&gt;vibranium<br />\niron man好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁當然，你可以話thanos只不過係力量大，所以先可以徒手破壞vibranium<br />\n但係宏觀marvel電影入面(唔計漫畫)目前除左thor個斧外同captain marvel(我都唔記得佢有無打到thanos見血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)外<br />\n都好似無邊個可以打到thanos流血(戴定頭盔先，因為電影院太暗所以睇唔清楚avengers4入面captain  america拎鎚有無打到佢流血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n但係以無超能力嘅普通人來講，只靠科技可以達成呢個成就，iron man真係好撚勁<br />\n仲要係avengers4入面做終結thanos嘅角色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />respect<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎大家一齊為iron man打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f5db6c5c5c99d686bbc7d850f43fb35284d41b","tid":1151534,"uid":246739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T14:55:04.000Z","msg":"正評係我比<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f9239b8885859c50db69967f34205c2d71727c","tid":1151534,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T14:57:07.000Z","msg":"邏輯錯誤<br />\n身體硬度同拎唔拎到粒石出黎係冇關係"}]}